          "action": "escalate_to_human",
          "handoffTarget": "Chief risk officer / reinsurance buying committee",
          "rationale": "PML swings of that size change reinsurance tower adequacy and rating-agency capital adequacy (BCAR) inputs, which are board-level risk decisions."
        }
